window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>Violet Archer's world is crumbling down around her. She's discovering things she never knew, and there's still more to come. Determined as she is, she's rolling with the punches and knocking out a few of her own.</p> <p>She's finding herself in the middle of, well, quite a few things. And as deeply tangled as she is with two very powerful men, she can't just walk away from either. </p> <p>She's also carrying a heavy burden, with the weight of two warring races on her shoulders, a prophecy to fulfill, and an item she must procure for the god of death.</p> <p>And none of it will be easy. </p> <p>Violet is going to have to make her way through some very dark places if there is any chance of finding the light.</p> <p><b>The Shadow Series is an epic fantasy and adult paranormal romance adventure set. Follow Violet's story as it continues in the third book of the series.</b></p> <p><b>Warning: This is a novel for adults. Contains mature and explicit content. Advisory warning for those with sensitivities or to issues regarding mental health and well-being.</b></p>"; 
